          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fly Smart Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes standards relating to airline travel by federal employees for official business, with a general ban on military aircraft for domestic travel, and with exceptions to such airline travel, such as to accommodate a disability or a special need that has been certified.</p>]]></text>
